716
00:51:18.528 --> 00:51:21.248
Dostoevsky said that
after doing a little time.

717
00:51:21.331 --> 00:51:25.686
"Fuck you!" Cyrus Grissom said that
after putting a bullet in my agent's head. Okay?

718
00:51:25.970 --> 00:51:28.589
The issue here is how the plane
is brought down.

719
00:51:28.672 --> 00:51:30.485
Shoot it down.

720
00:51:30.716 --> 00:51:34.720
Yeah. When exactly did this
become a DEA jurisdiction?

721
00:51:34.803 --> 00:51:37.431
The second the DEA agent
