00:53:04.092 --> 00:53:06.149
Hillbilly!

747
00:53:06.178 --> 00:53:07.933
Poe.

748
00:53:12.484 --> 00:53:13.333
Yeah?

749
00:53:13.584 --> 00:53:16.427
Cyrus wants you to check out
the landing gear.

750
00:53:16.462 --> 00:53:19.855
