751
00:53:24.997 --> 00:53:26.874
Trees and stuff.

752
00:53:47.209 --> 00:53:50.230
Goddamn! So that's
what happened to Pinball.

753
00:53:50.472 --> 00:53:53.767
Cut him loose. He's slowin'
us down. Dead weight.

