819
00:58:49.696 --> 00:58:54.451
Uh, maybe, if you... if you do
see him or if you talk to him,

820
00:58:54.576 --> 00:58:58.747
maybe you could just...
tell him to come home, all right?

821
00:58:58.872 --> 00:59:01.208
Be kinda nice
