822
00:59:02.251 --> 00:59:03.984
You got it.

823
00:59:05.295 --> 00:59:07.464
Vince, line one.

824
00:59:09.800 --> 00:59:11.885
This body fell out
of the sky.

825
00:59:11.927 --> 00:59:16.223
Vince Larkin? This is Ted Grasso,
Fresno Police Department.

826
00:59:16.306 --> 00:59:18.438
<i>We got a problem here
with a corpse.</i>

827
00:59:18.797 --> 00:59:19.549
Uh-huh.

828
00:59:19.902 --> 00:59:21.570
<i>Yeah, it fell out of the sky.</i>

