904
01:06:14.433 --> 01:06:16.477
Oh, my God.

905
01:06:16.771 --> 01:06:18.172
Look out!

906
01:07:33.136 --> 01:07:35.973
Lerner Airfield.
I'm so glad to be here.

907
01:07:39.184 --> 01:07:41.937
Thank you
for choosing Con Air.

